995822c04e8e53966239e7dd8b27480d562e1481ae4fca0b3debce2a950fc82326762c7595b8e2cab0f51301370328839ceec5a6bc43c2f76663a0a4d921163b  0001-driver-apdu-qmi-Pass-correct-open-flag-for-QRTR-driv.patch
"
